author: Justin Anastos <justin.anastos@gmail.com>
description: Demo of webpack working with videojs-contrib-dash
name: webpack-videojs-contrib-dash

scripts.start: NODE_ENV=development nodemon --watch webpack.config.babel.js --watch .babelrc $(npm bin)/babel-node $(npm bin)/webpack-dev-server --config webpack.config.babel.js -d --colors --progress --no-info --hot --inline --port 8090 --host=0.0.0.0 --display-error-details --content-base src
